column1: This EF3 device is the third-generation FPGA product from Anlogic for communication, industrial control, and server markets, supporting up to 336 user I/Os. It adopts an advanced 55nm low-power process that optimizes power and performance while enabling high functionality at reduced cost. Designed for large-scale, cost-sensitive applications, it helps meet increasing bandwidth requirements. Comprehensive design tools further assist users in effectively implementing complex designs on the EF3 platform.
